, "ar", "learn"], "long_description": "\nTraceARtist is an augmented reality application for Meta Quest 3 that overlays images onto the user's physical environment for tracing purposes.\nUsers can trace these digital images directly on paper or other drawing surfaces.\nThe app offers both pre-loaded image categories and support for custom uploads, providing a versatile digital reference tool for artists.\n# Key features include:\n\n- **Diverse image sources**: pre-loaded collections with high quality images in lossless SVG format (famous paintings, architecture/castles, animals), and support for custom uploads\n- **Spatial anchoring** for consistent image placement\n- **Environmental integration** with shadow rendering and collision detection\n- **Drawing assistance tools**: opacity adjustment, desk calibration, and intuitive image manipulation\n\nTraceARtist is optimized for Meta Quest 3, offering native resolution support and a responsive AR environment. It accommodates artists of all skill levels, from beginners to experienced professionals.\n\nFor technical support or inquiries: \n\ntraceartistapp@gmail.com\n", "short_description": "TraceARtist is a Meta Quest 3 app that overlays digital images onto real-world surfaces for direct paper drawing. This AR tool bridges traditional techniques with mixed reality, helping artists of all levels enhance their skills through digital-to-physical creation."}]}, "developer_name": "RedShedD", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://traceartist.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "RedShedD", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://traceartist.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "323450648956687"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "